_sText:
de_saw  - Bomb/Defuse

Updated the old custom map by 'jackennils'

Features: 
  • New Layout to improve balance
  • Moved T-spawn closer to A site
  • Removed some scripted sequences ('Stairs trap' for Example)
  • Added/moved some props for cover
  • Radio room entrance to middle now connects with B-site passage
  • CT-spawn moved downstairs, 'Jigsaw' computer room is blocked now
  • Blocked doorway from CT-spawn to the outside grass area
  • New entrance from T-Outside to B-site passage area (old one removed)
  • Blocked sewer passage from T-Outside to Freezer area
  • B-site narrow hall now shorter and connects with surgery room
  • Removed Vent entrance to B-Site
  • Removed some hiding spots on B-Site
  • A-Site moved on 2nd floor of the 'House'
  • 3rd floor now blocked
  • Removed vent passages leading to A-Site
  • Added drop-room with ladder instead of Vent ladder passage
  • Added ladder-shelf on the first floor of the 'House'
  • Vent passage to the 'Furnace' basement is taller now
  • Removed some doors, breakable walls for better navigation
  • Added doorway to graveyard hall under A-Site room
  • Bot support 
  • Overview
